1
00:00:01,800 --> 00:00:05,637
Let's end it.

2
00:00:06,240 --> 00:00:07,664
What?

3
00:00:08,280 --> 00:00:09,974
I'm sorry.

4
00:00:11,840 --> 00:00:17,715
After that, I gave it much consideration.

5
00:00:17,715 --> 00:00:23,223
I hope that I can become a good wife to you someday.

6
00:00:23,223 --> 00:00:26,230
I want to work hard to become Nijiro-kun's mother.

7
00:00:26,230 --> 00:00:28,596
You don't have to do it.

8
00:00:30,420 --> 00:00:35,431
Because you will not be the Kyoka-san that I know.

9
00:00:35,930 --> 00:00:36,819
However...

10
00:00:36,819 --> 00:00:38,784
It's not possible.

11
00:00:38,784 --> 00:00:43,021
I can't continue this relationship anymore.

12
00:00:44,740 --> 00:00:48,615
Previously, I wanted a wife who would change my clothes.

13
00:00:48,615 --> 00:00:50,817
Didn't I say that?

14
00:00:51,780 --> 00:00:57,416
Originally, I didn't want a normal marriage,

15
00:00:57,416 --> 00:00:59,754
it is just impossible

16
00:01:01,630 --> 00:01:03,504
for me to continue.

17
00:01:05,560 --> 00:01:07,667
It's my fault.

18
00:01:07,667 --> 00:01:11,197
I already knew that things would not go well, but...

19
00:01:11,197 --> 00:01:13,148
Seita-san.

20
00:01:14,470 --> 00:01:16,476
It was an enjoyable time.

21
00:01:18,440 --> 00:01:20,714
Thank you.

22
00:01:22,210 --> 00:01:25,884
And I'm really sorry.

23
00:01:41,140 --> 00:01:50,410
<i>Timing and Subtitles brought to you by
Sustainable Heartbeats Team @Viki.com </i>

24
00:01:50,410 --> 00:01:52,312
What's wrong?

25
00:01:52,312 --> 00:01:54,963
I reject to our dating.

26
00:01:56,380 --> 00:01:58,477
I'm sorry.

27
00:02:02,500 --> 00:02:04,323
Excuse me,

28
00:02:08,120 --> 00:02:10,190
but can I know the reason?

29
00:02:12,290 --> 00:02:17,103
You can be happy under normal circumstances.

30
00:02:18,210 --> 00:02:20,178
I'm not good enough for you.

31
00:02:24,300 --> 00:02:26,500
Thank you for everything.

32
00:02:41,610 --> 00:02:43,217
Welcome home.

33
00:02:45,390 --> 00:02:47,067
You're late today,

34
00:02:47,067 --> 00:02:49,102
though it's fine with me.

35
00:02:49,610 --> 00:02:51,519
Did you go out with Higashimura-san?

36
00:02:53,270 --> 00:02:54,870
I see.

37
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:59,312
He's a good person.

38
00:03:00,010 --> 00:03:02,511
I think so, too.

39
00:03:02,511 --> 00:03:04,144
That's good.

40
00:03:05,230 --> 00:03:06,842
Goodnight.

41
00:03:20,538 --> 00:03:29,297
<i>[Is Love Sustainable?]</i>
<i>[Episode 9]</i>

42
00:03:29,980 --> 00:03:32,813
Did Sawada-san reject you?

43
00:03:32,813 --> 00:03:38,457
Yes. I think I do not appeal to him at all.

44
00:03:38,457 --> 00:03:41,303
I give up on getting married.

45
00:03:41,303 --> 00:03:43,623
You don't have to give up.

46
00:03:43,623 --> 00:03:49,195
Anyway, I think I will stop marriage hunting for the moment.

47
00:03:50,530 --> 00:03:53,530
A rejection might not mean

48
00:03:53,530 --> 00:03:57,637
that he is not satisfied with you.

49
00:03:57,637 --> 00:04:01,946
Sometimes it might be due to consideration that not getting married is better for the other party.

50
00:04:01,946 --> 00:04:03,376
I understand that.

51
00:04:03,376 --> 00:04:07,011
Sawada-san is probably worried about his age,

52
00:04:07,011 --> 00:04:09,741
my first marriage and his remarrying,

53
00:04:09,741 --> 00:04:14,410
and he has many other considerations for my sake.

54
00:04:15,320 --> 00:04:19,797
But I hope that he could be strong enough

55
00:04:19,797 --> 00:04:23,129
to overcome his own kindness and rationale.

56
00:04:23,670 --> 00:04:26,945
Because I'm really thinking about marriage.

57
00:04:30,170 --> 00:04:33,042
What does happiness mean, in normal circumstance?

58
00:04:33,670 --> 00:04:35,342
In normal circumstance?

59
00:04:36,800 --> 00:04:40,879
Please excuse me my question.

60
00:04:45,100 --> 00:04:48,430
Hello. Sorry to disturb.

61
00:04:48,430 --> 00:04:50,810
Thank you for doing the check for me.

62
00:04:50,810 --> 00:04:54,125
About the tumor biopsy result,

63
00:04:54,125 --> 00:04:56,896
it takes about a week.

64
00:04:56,896 --> 00:05:00,898
Then can you schedule the next consultation when the results are out?

65
00:05:02,230 --> 00:05:03,931
Thank you.

66
00:05:04,640 --> 00:05:06,698
Okay, see you.

67
00:05:15,840 --> 00:05:19,537
Place your fingers together behind your back.

68
00:05:19,537 --> 00:05:23,477
If you can do it easily, you can flip your palm over.

69
00:05:24,890 --> 00:05:30,229
Open your chest up for that slouch during desk work.

70
00:05:45,030 --> 00:05:47,952
The turtle parent and child.

71
00:05:47,952 --> 00:05:50,771
That cloud looks like a turtle.

72
00:05:50,771 --> 00:05:52,285
Doesn't it?

73
00:06:00,397 --> 00:06:02,962
<i>[Fuwa Hayate]
[Meet tonight?]</i>

74
00:06:02,962 --> 00:06:06,212
This is good. Try it.

75
00:06:06,212 --> 00:06:07,512
Really?

76
00:06:09,810 --> 00:06:12,571
- This is really good.
- Right?

77
00:06:16,977 --> 00:06:19,780
I really appreciate what you did.

78
00:06:19,780 --> 00:06:20,891
No worries.

79
00:06:20,891 --> 00:06:23,101
Nijiro has already cheered up.

80
00:06:23,101 --> 00:06:26,237
He was really noisy in school today.

81
00:06:26,237 --> 00:06:28,049
I see.

82
00:06:33,930 --> 00:06:35,872
How is it with Higashimura-san and you?

83
00:06:36,430 --> 00:06:37,811
What?

84
00:06:40,790 --> 00:06:42,685
I was dumped.

85
00:06:47,540 --> 00:06:50,743
But I'm totally fine.

86
00:06:51,540 --> 00:06:56,917
For now, I still need to buck up in my work.

87
00:06:56,917 --> 00:06:59,020
Love does not matter anymore.

88
00:06:59,450 --> 00:07:02,956
This time, I was shaken up

89
00:07:02,956 --> 00:07:05,281
and it affected my work.

90
00:07:07,590 --> 00:07:09,730
I need to live again with my job.

91
00:07:09,730 --> 00:07:11,565
Kyoka-chan.

92
00:07:12,030 --> 00:07:15,267
Office yoga is going well.

93
00:07:15,267 --> 00:07:17,904
My students recommended me to other companies,

94
00:07:17,904 --> 00:07:19,909
and I've been asked to open my own studio.

95
00:07:19,909 --> 00:07:21,315
Kyoka-chan.

96
00:07:21,315 --> 00:07:23,577
My followers on Instagram also increased.

97
00:07:23,577 --> 00:07:27,065
If one-tenth of my followers become my students,

98
00:07:27,065 --> 00:07:28,846
I'll be able to maintain my own studio.

99
00:07:28,846 --> 00:07:30,073
Kyoka-chan.

100
00:07:30,073 --> 00:07:33,084
But I'm wondering if I should do online yoga.

101
00:07:33,084 --> 00:07:35,805
- Kyoka-chan...
- Excuse me, can I have two beers?

102
00:07:35,805 --> 00:07:37,603
Yes, no problem.

103
00:07:37,603 --> 00:07:40,639
Let's drink today, okay?

104
00:07:48,760 --> 00:07:50,269
The moon is beautiful.

105
00:07:51,970 --> 00:07:53,933
I'll take a photo.

106
00:07:53,933 --> 00:07:56,525
I need to upload it on Instagram.

107
00:07:58,070 --> 00:07:59,520
Okay.

108
00:08:00,846 --> 00:08:02,710
It doesn't look good.

109
00:08:07,170 --> 00:08:09,397
The photo didn't turn out well.

110
00:08:11,190 --> 00:08:13,386
I wonder how I can take it beautifully.

111
00:08:13,386 --> 00:08:15,059
Kyoka-chan.

112
00:08:16,120 --> 00:08:18,258
This has become mandatory.

113
00:08:18,258 --> 00:08:21,527
Well, this is part of the marketing.

114
00:08:23,160 --> 00:08:25,409
Look, this is very convenient.

115
00:08:25,409 --> 00:08:27,306
Thank you.

116
00:08:28,170 --> 00:08:30,973
It's okay not to be smiling all the time.

117
00:08:30,973 --> 00:08:34,470
You can sulk and pout, or even slack in your work.

118
00:08:34,470 --> 00:08:36,394
Even if you were to lose your smartphone,

119
00:08:36,394 --> 00:08:39,402
people will not dislike you.

120
00:08:41,270 --> 00:08:43,202
You are a good person,

121
00:08:43,202 --> 00:08:46,138
and I know that you are a good woman now.

122
00:08:46,610 --> 00:08:48,298
Hayate.

123
00:08:56,960 --> 00:09:00,406
I'm glad to have a childhood friend like you.

124
00:09:01,640 --> 00:09:03,143
Thank you.

125
00:09:03,143 --> 00:09:05,304
Then, goodnight.

126
00:09:05,304 --> 00:09:06,902
See you.

127
00:09:13,850 --> 00:09:16,589
So, you've been approved of shorter working hours?

128
00:09:17,080 --> 00:09:19,502
Thank you.

129
00:09:21,140 --> 00:09:24,673
But is that really what you want?

130
00:09:25,240 --> 00:09:28,925
Didn't they say that you won't be able to go back to the headquarters?

131
00:09:28,925 --> 00:09:31,115
Well, I'm fine with that.

132
00:09:31,115 --> 00:09:33,248
As long as I can receive child support.

133
00:09:33,248 --> 00:09:37,151
You don't need to worry about going to Osaka.

134
00:09:37,151 --> 00:09:41,128
I understand. I'll keep my promise.

135
00:09:41,128 --> 00:09:44,123
Papa, can I eat ice-cream?

136
00:09:44,123 --> 00:09:46,891
Of course not. You just brushed your teeth, right?

137
00:09:49,100 --> 00:09:54,059
Nijiro said it's fine for me to go to Osaka,

138
00:09:55,460 --> 00:09:57,674
but I wonder how he really feels.

139
00:09:57,674 --> 00:10:01,767
I'll talk to him again.

140
00:10:01,767 --> 00:10:03,413
Thank you.

141
00:10:03,413 --> 00:10:04,997
Another thing I want to ask,

142
00:10:07,520 --> 00:10:09,671
how's your relationship with Kyoka-san?

143
00:10:09,671 --> 00:10:13,379
We drew a clear line.

144
00:10:13,379 --> 00:10:15,259
Look what I have!

145
00:10:15,259 --> 00:10:18,404
Hey, Niji.

146
00:10:18,404 --> 00:10:21,955
I will brush my teeth again later.

147
00:10:21,955 --> 00:10:25,224
Say thanks to yourself.

148
00:10:25,224 --> 00:10:30,092
Thank you.

149
00:10:30,092 --> 00:10:34,200
This will end our lesson today.

150
00:10:43,200 --> 00:10:46,107
Sorry for the sudden visit.

151
00:10:47,910 --> 00:10:52,963
I've heard about the panel yoga.

152
00:10:54,650 --> 00:10:58,848
Nijiro had a fever on the day that you did not go for the meeting, right?

153
00:11:00,680 --> 00:11:01,862
I'm really sorry about it.

154
00:11:01,862 --> 00:11:04,417
I made the decision myself.

155
00:11:04,960 --> 00:11:09,654
And I won't meet Nijiro-kun again.

156
00:11:09,654 --> 00:11:12,375
I'm sorry to have caused a fuss.

157
00:11:13,800 --> 00:11:18,180
- Kyoka-san, is that really all right with you?
- Work is my first priority now.

158
00:11:18,180 --> 00:11:23,180
I will try to my best to be independent in my yoga job.

159
00:11:25,170 --> 00:11:28,221
Sorry that I couldn't help in any way.

160
00:11:28,221 --> 00:11:33,445
No. You've helped by telling me so much.

161
00:11:34,520 --> 00:11:35,963
About missing the meeting,

162
00:11:36,570 --> 00:11:40,503
can you keep it from Seita-san?

163
00:11:42,030 --> 00:11:43,159
That's not...

164
00:11:43,159 --> 00:11:44,659
Please.

165
00:11:57,380 --> 00:12:00,127
- Please take care.
- Thank you.

166
00:12:01,980 --> 00:12:05,416
Doctor, you've had a long day.

167
00:12:05,416 --> 00:12:08,851
It's already late, but what about lunch?

168
00:12:08,851 --> 00:12:11,130
I have no appetite.

169
00:12:11,130 --> 00:12:13,455
You look tired.

170
00:12:15,560 --> 00:12:17,994
It's tough to be rejected at this age.

171
00:12:17,994 --> 00:12:20,511
What?! You were rejected by the other party?

172
00:12:20,511 --> 00:12:23,526
Yes, now I'm reminded of it again.

173
00:12:23,526 --> 00:12:25,886
My chest still hurts from being rejected.

174
00:12:30,890 --> 00:12:33,330
Doctor, are you all right?

175
00:12:33,330 --> 00:12:35,189
Should I call the ambulance?

176
00:12:35,189 --> 00:12:36,943
I'm all right.

177
00:12:38,490 --> 00:12:41,629
So, it has not ended well with the single father.

178
00:12:41,629 --> 00:12:44,264
- Yes.
- It must be difficult for you.

179
00:12:44,264 --> 00:12:45,966
Well...

180
00:12:46,530 --> 00:12:49,601
Aren't you eating a bit too much?

181
00:12:50,330 --> 00:12:52,538
You eat some, too.

182
00:12:53,370 --> 00:12:56,101
Even though you are dumped, you still need to have a life.

183
00:12:56,101 --> 00:12:58,712
I'm eating. Don't worry.

184
00:12:58,712 --> 00:13:01,413
I only returned to who I was originally.

185
00:13:01,413 --> 00:13:05,316
No wish for marriage. My dream comes first.

186
00:13:05,316 --> 00:13:07,545
You don't even want to fall in love, right?

187
00:13:07,545 --> 00:13:10,590
You've surpassed your original self.

188
00:13:10,590 --> 00:13:12,735
Sorry I'm late.

189
00:13:12,735 --> 00:13:14,794
You must have had a tough day.

190
00:13:14,794 --> 00:13:17,389
- Is Hinata-san okay?
- Yes.

191
00:13:17,389 --> 00:13:20,334
But she needs to be hospitalized today.

192
00:13:20,334 --> 00:13:23,682
I see. Hope she will be fine.

193
00:13:23,682 --> 00:13:26,251
- How about the clinic?
- It will be closed for a week.

194
00:13:26,251 --> 00:13:28,553
Excuse me, beer please.

195
00:13:33,740 --> 00:13:35,148
It's piping hot!

196
00:13:35,148 --> 00:13:37,552
- Good morning.
- Good morning.

197
00:13:38,580 --> 00:13:40,687
What is that? What happened?

198
00:13:40,687 --> 00:13:44,590
I can do this myself. You came home late yesterday, right?

199
00:13:45,080 --> 00:13:46,738
Did you go out with Higashimura-san?

200
00:13:46,738 --> 00:13:48,845
- What?
- Aren't you two going out?

201
00:13:48,845 --> 00:13:53,399
I will settle my breakfast myself.

202
00:13:53,399 --> 00:13:56,635
If you were to leave this house,

203
00:13:56,635 --> 00:14:00,138
I will need to live by myself.

204
00:14:02,040 --> 00:14:03,984
It's ended.

205
00:14:03,984 --> 00:14:05,689
Eh?

206
00:14:05,689 --> 00:14:09,114
And it's just started not long ago, so it's not really important.

207
00:14:09,114 --> 00:14:10,921
You've liked him, so why?

208
00:14:10,921 --> 00:14:13,686
That reminds me. Father, do you know?

209
00:14:13,686 --> 00:14:15,194
Hinata-san is hospitalized.

210
00:14:15,194 --> 00:14:17,546
Don't change the topic.

211
00:14:17,546 --> 00:14:19,045
- Eh?
- Yesterday.

212
00:14:19,045 --> 00:14:21,732
Suzu said she collapsed in the clinic.

213
00:14:21,732 --> 00:14:23,577
Collapsed?

214
00:14:23,577 --> 00:14:25,932
- Yes.
- What sickness is she suffering from? How is she now?

215
00:14:25,932 --> 00:14:30,169
I don't know about that. I just know that she's hospitalized.

216
00:14:33,210 --> 00:14:36,576
Don't tell me the person that you like...

217
00:14:36,576 --> 00:14:38,378
Which hospital is she in?

218
00:14:58,350 --> 00:15:00,135
Hinata-san.

219
00:15:01,030 --> 00:15:02,602
Sawada-san.

220
00:15:02,602 --> 00:15:04,763
Sorry to visit without informing.

221
00:15:04,763 --> 00:15:05,849
No worries.

222
00:15:05,849 --> 00:15:09,041
Sorry, but I heard that you collapsed, so I had to...

223
00:15:11,520 --> 00:15:15,213
How are you feeling?

224
00:15:15,213 --> 00:15:17,239
It's due to overworking.

225
00:15:17,239 --> 00:15:20,184
So, you are hospitalized just due to overworking?

226
00:15:22,590 --> 00:15:28,190
Actually, a tumour in my chest was found during a check-up,

227
00:15:28,190 --> 00:15:31,717
and I'm waiting for the biopsy results.

228
00:15:31,717 --> 00:15:33,522
Then suddenly, I felt dizzy...

229
00:15:34,960 --> 00:15:37,847
So, I'm unable to continue with marriage hunting for a while.

230
00:15:37,847 --> 00:15:39,460
Excuse me.

231
00:15:44,670 --> 00:15:47,614
Sorry for being imprudent,

232
00:15:47,614 --> 00:15:50,386
but I would like to take my words back.

233
00:15:54,080 --> 00:15:55,558
If you...

234
00:15:56,680 --> 00:16:00,781
If your feelings have not changed,

235
00:16:01,870 --> 00:16:04,242
I would like to date you.

236
00:16:05,120 --> 00:16:07,278
I reject your offer.

237
00:16:07,278 --> 00:16:08,418
Eh?

238
00:16:08,418 --> 00:16:12,981
If the result shows a problem, I would only be a burden to you.

239
00:16:13,740 --> 00:16:16,247
I'm now in this state,

240
00:16:16,247 --> 00:16:19,247
so you are just... taking pity on me.

241
00:16:19,247 --> 00:16:22,572
No, you are mistaken.

242
00:16:24,610 --> 00:16:26,368
But to think that you might be gone,

243
00:16:27,120 --> 00:16:33,403
I won't be able to take it.

244
00:16:35,620 --> 00:16:40,586
I would like to continue my life together with you.

245
00:16:41,800 --> 00:16:46,603
If I can live in this world together with you,

246
00:16:47,610 --> 00:16:49,160
I mean if it's possible,

247
00:16:50,860 --> 00:16:53,291
I will be a happy man.

248
00:16:54,600 --> 00:16:56,405
I also hope that

249
00:16:59,110 --> 00:17:01,988
you can share my happiness.

250
00:17:10,960 --> 00:17:12,935
If it's really possible,

251
00:17:14,660 --> 00:17:17,202
I will also be happy.

252
00:17:21,300 --> 00:17:25,410
Be happy as normal.

253
00:17:27,040 --> 00:17:28,820
Hinata-san.

254
00:17:32,020 --> 00:17:34,625
Please take good care of me.

255
00:17:35,470 --> 00:17:37,398
I'll be looking forward.

256
00:17:48,960 --> 00:17:53,705
Excuse me, Dr. Matsuo wants to see you.

257
00:17:54,790 --> 00:17:56,408
Okay.

258
00:18:00,960 --> 00:18:04,350
<i>[Conference Room]</i>

259
00:18:16,131 --> 00:18:17,363
Menopause?

260
00:18:17,363 --> 00:18:19,599
I'll go straight to the point.

261
00:18:19,599 --> 00:18:23,804
The tumor is benign, and there are no other problems.

262
00:18:23,804 --> 00:18:26,406
However, look at this.

263
00:18:26,406 --> 00:18:29,557
Really, the oestradiol count is low.

264
00:18:29,557 --> 00:18:31,811
It's a bit early,

265
00:18:31,811 --> 00:18:35,272
but we've reached that age.

266
00:18:35,272 --> 00:18:38,485
Replenishing your hormones will make it better.

267
00:18:38,485 --> 00:18:42,595
So, that's why.

268
00:18:42,595 --> 00:18:46,036
Dizziness, sleeplessness and heart palpitations,

269
00:18:47,210 --> 00:18:51,215
what about the feeling in my chest?

270
00:18:52,130 --> 00:18:54,945
Did I make a mistake?

271
