287
00:19:57,874 --> 00:19:59,944
Regarding the matter with Higashimura-san and you...

288
00:19:59,944 --> 00:20:02,546
That's enough.

289
00:20:02,546 --> 00:20:04,245
I found it.

290
00:20:04,910 --> 00:20:09,920
