293
00:20:17,599 --> 00:20:19,493
Happy as a normal person?

294
00:20:20,500 --> 00:20:22,723
Hey, Kyoka. Don't tell me it's because of...

295
00:20:22,723 --> 00:20:25,893
We really don't know what to expect in life.

296
00:20:25,893 --> 00:20:30,611
In the beginning, you started marriage hunting because of me.

297
00:20:31,200 --> 00:20:35,979
