304
00:20:57,840 --> 00:20:59,012
No, I did not.

305
00:20:59,012 --> 00:21:00,277
No?

306
00:21:00,277 --> 00:21:02,229
Yes, I did not.

307
00:21:02,229 --> 00:21:04,480
<i>[Hinata Akari-sama]</i>

308
00:21:04,480 --> 00:21:05,940
<i>Good evening.</i>

309
00:21:05,940 --> 00:21:10,514
<i>I'm glad that you have been discharged safely.</i>

310
00:21:10,514 --> 00:21:14,784
<i>Today, I would like to tell you about how I feel,</i>

311
00:21:14,784 --> 00:21:19,673
<i>thus I am writing this mail to you.</i>

312
00:21:23,040 --> 00:21:27,931
<i>I like you, Hinata Akari-san.</i>

313
00:21:27,931 --> 00:21:30,350
