363
00:24:12,985 --> 00:24:16,306
Ah, a full moon in June...

364
00:24:16,306 --> 00:24:18,070
I think it's a strawberry moon.

365
00:24:18,070 --> 00:24:20,092
Yes, it is.

366
00:24:20,092 --> 00:24:22,541
You really know a lot.

367
00:24:22,541 --> 00:24:25,320
Send me the venue later.

368
00:24:25,320 --> 00:24:27,466
Okay.

369
00:24:27,466 --> 00:24:31,803
Hey, do you want to come for dinner tomorrow?

370
00:24:31,803 --> 00:24:33,673
We have a celebration to make.

371
00:24:33,673 --> 00:24:35,173
A celebration?

372
00:24:36,650 --> 00:24:37,980
Hayate.

373
00:24:37,980 --> 00:24:39,942
Uncle!

374
00:24:39,942 --> 00:24:42,881
Congratulations!

375
00:24:42,881 --> 00:24:44,651
