396
00:25:49,833 --> 00:25:51,786
That's right.

397
00:25:52,650 --> 00:25:57,255
Father is also more independent now.

398
00:25:57,255 --> 00:25:59,109
So, things will go well, right?

399
00:25:59,920 --> 00:26:02,434
