420
00:27:30,550 --> 00:27:33,212
It would be a great help if you are around.

421
00:27:33,212 --> 00:27:35,450
I don't mean that.

422
00:27:38,130 --> 00:27:44,230
If you are going to be alone, I'd feel troubled.

423
00:27:54,210 --> 00:27:55,962
Goodnight.

424
00:28:12,200 --> 00:28:14,053
Yoko-san.

425
00:28:15,160 --> 00:28:18,600
There's a change of plans.

426
00:28:24,030 --> 00:28:26,833
Is that so? I'm happy to hear.

427
00:28:26,833 --> 00:28:29,333
Congratulations on proceeding to a serious relationship.

428
00:28:29,333 --> 00:28:30,657
Thank you.

429
00:28:30,657 --> 00:28:33,903
I'm really happy to hear the good news.

430
00:28:36,280 --> 00:28:39,439
I heard from Kyoka.

431
00:28:39,990 --> 00:28:42,937
Her relationship with you...

432
00:28:42,937 --> 00:28:44,850
It's a pity.

433
00:28:46,590 --> 00:28:48,095
I'm sorry.

434
00:28:48,095 --> 00:28:50,365
No, you don't need to be.

435
00:28:52,798 --> 00:28:55,658
When my ex-wife passed away,

436
00:28:55,658 --> 00:28:59,354
I wanted Kyoka to be happy.

437
00:28:59,354 --> 00:29:02,421
And we've received much concern from your company.

438
00:29:04,570 --> 00:29:09,349
