440
00:29:14,100 --> 00:29:15,596
I'm sorry about it.

441
00:29:15,596 --> 00:29:17,260
No, it's fine.

442
00:29:18,390 --> 00:29:22,966
It's also my fault

443
00:29:22,966 --> 00:29:25,805
