444
00:29:27,410 --> 00:29:29,368
but there's a reason behind it.

445
00:29:29,368 --> 00:29:31,045
A reason?

446
00:29:31,045 --> 00:29:32,711
Yes.

447
00:29:35,010 --> 00:29:37,029
Actually...

448
