00:30:06,152 --> 00:30:07,735
Yes.

457
00:30:09,020 --> 00:30:11,523
But don't worry about it.

458
00:30:11,523 --> 00:30:14,543
She's moving on independently, so you don't need to worry.

459
00:30:15,970 --> 00:30:18,794
It seems that she's going to live alone.

460
00:30:18,794 --> 00:30:20,533
How did you know about it?

461
00:30:20,533 --> 00:30:22,033
That's because...

462
00:30:23,350 --> 00:30:26,509
You'd better not get involved half-heartedly.

463
00:30:26,509 --> 00:30:28,338
And you don't need to be kind to her.

464
00:30:28,338 --> 00:30:30,631
Nijiro, get prepared to go.

465
00:30:30,631 --> 00:30:32,438
Yes.

466
00:30:32,438 --> 00:30:35,280
Nijiro, it's time to go home.

467
00:30:35,280 --> 00:30:37,110
Okay.

468
00:30:46,430 --> 00:30:49,539
