473
00:31:04,129 --> 00:31:06,007
Yes, I did.

474
00:31:06,007 --> 00:31:07,936
But you don't have to answer that.

475
00:31:07,936 --> 00:31:10,166
I have no interest in marriage now.

476
00:31:11,040 --> 00:31:13,863
I thought the same, too.

477
00:31:13,863 --> 00:31:15,173
Eh?

478
00:31:15,173 --> 00:31:18,710
I wanted to know the meaning of marriage,

479
00:31:18,710 --> 00:31:20,514
