480
00:31:20,514 --> 00:31:22,515
What are you talking about?

481
00:31:23,080 --> 00:31:26,418
Yoko-san was my junior at the seminar class at university.

482
00:31:26,418 --> 00:31:28,717
She was cheerful and popular with the guys.

483
00:31:28,717 --> 00:31:31,714
However, I did not know her well.

484
00:31:31,714 --> 00:31:35,814
I guess that. She's totally different from you.

485
00:31:36,350 --> 00:31:41,600
Therefore, that day was seven years after I graduated.

486
00:31:42,930 --> 00:31:46,840
At that time, I was just a poor university lecturer,

487
00:31:46,840 --> 00:31:50,944
