489
00:31:57,690 --> 00:32:00,044
You can see for yourself.

490
00:32:00,700 --> 00:32:02,731
Please excuse me.

491
00:32:04,960 --> 00:32:10,000
Sawada-kun, you are honest and hardworking.

492
00:32:10,000 --> 00:32:13,569
