496
00:32:27,230 --> 00:32:29,871
Why is that so?

497
00:32:30,450 --> 00:32:34,859
Because you are not living a life.

498
00:32:35,750 --> 00:32:39,989
Words are not just in the books,

499
00:32:39,989 --> 00:32:44,229
