500
00:32:45,060 --> 00:32:47,232
Alive?

501
00:32:47,232 --> 00:32:52,565
Sawada-kun, how would you explain

502
00:32:52,565 --> 00:32:55,667
the word "alive"?

503
00:32:57,750 --> 00:33:03,454
Breathing and in existence.

504
00:33:05,290 --> 00:33:08,361
