505
00:33:11,170 --> 00:33:14,019
Something that is ever-changing.

506
00:33:14,990 --> 00:33:17,180
How is that?

507
00:33:17,180 --> 00:33:19,995
Ever-changing?

508
00:33:21,730 --> 00:33:25,269
Live your life to the fullest.

509
00:33:26,350 --> 00:33:30,074
I was unable to say anything.

510
00:33:30,074 --> 00:33:34,279
I didn't connect with people and just indulged myself in books.

511
00:33:34,279 --> 00:33:37,856
I didn't laugh with anyone, nor had any quarrels.

512
00:33:37,856 --> 00:33:41,483
I just lived day by day the same way as I did the day before.

513
00:33:43,920 --> 00:33:46,556
