523
00:34:18,390 --> 00:34:20,554
Are you all right?

524
00:34:20,554 --> 00:34:22,563
I'm fine.

525
00:34:26,800 --> 00:34:29,379
- I'll go call a nurse.
- No, I'm fine.

526
00:34:29,379 --> 00:34:30,820
I just need to take a rest.

527
00:34:30,820 --> 00:34:32,671
Should I get you some water?

528
00:34:32,671 --> 00:34:34,536
It's okay.

529
00:34:37,270 --> 00:34:41,647
Is there anything that I can help?

530
00:34:41,647 --> 00:34:43,493
Then...

531
00:34:44,810 --> 00:34:47,852
