532
00:34:53,980 --> 00:34:57,107
Ah, I'm so sorry.

533
00:34:57,107 --> 00:35:00,155
Please ignore me. You can just leave.

534
00:35:02,430 --> 00:35:04,332
Okay.

535
00:35:10,950 --> 00:35:12,604
Okay.

536
00:35:13,360 --> 00:35:15,447
Let's get married.

537
