That time,

540
00:35:29,363 --> 00:35:32,143
if I did not meet Yoko-san,

541
00:35:33,170 --> 00:35:36,655
I would still be buried in the books.

542
00:35:37,870 --> 00:35:41,457
I would have no chance to quarrel with you.

543
00:35:43,360 --> 00:35:46,931
That was the moment of my life.

544
00:35:47,740 --> 00:35:49,782
During that time,

545
00:35:50,600 --> 00:35:54,222
the baby in Mother's stomach was?

546
00:35:56,050 --> 00:35:57,895
It's you.

547
00:35:59,280 --> 00:36:00,358
No way.

548
00:36:00,358 --> 00:36:05,356
Your mother found out that she was pregnant after breaking up with her boyfriend at that time.

549
00:36:05,356 --> 00:36:07,727
She thought of giving birth to the baby alone.

550
00:36:09,040 --> 00:36:11,607
However, she was not in her pink of health.

551
00:36:15,100 --> 00:36:19,939
If anything were to happen to her,

552
00:36:20,680 --> 00:36:23,515
she wanted someone to look after her child.

553
00:36:24,850 --> 00:36:26,585
So,

554
00:36:27,420 --> 00:36:30,255
Father and I...

555
00:36:30,255 --> 00:36:34,796
Yes, we are not related by blood.

556
00:36:38,863 --> 00:36:41,927
<i>Rintaro-san,</i>

557
00:36:41,927 --> 00:36:45,387
<i>thank you for accepting my proposal that day.</i>

558
00:36:48,220 --> 00:36:50,900
The meaning of marriage?

559
00:36:50,900 --> 00:36:52,551
<i>Regarding that,</i>

560
00:36:52,551 --> 00:36:54,617
<i>I still do not know.</i>

561
00:36:57,710 --> 00:37:02,154
I know the whereabouts of your real father.

562
00:37:12,810 --> 00:37:14,811
Father.

563
00:37:18,960 --> 00:37:21,039
Father...

564
00:37:22,110 --> 00:37:24,168
Yes, I am your father.

565
00:37:28,400 --> 00:37:34,917
Actually, I was intending to tell you upon your graduation,

566
00:37:35,480 --> 00:37:37,633
but I wasn't able to say it.

567
00:37:38,690 --> 00:37:40,104
Rintaro-san.

568
00:37:40,104 --> 00:37:41,250
Yes?

569
00:37:41,250 --> 00:37:43,262
About Kyoka...

570
00:37:43,262 --> 00:37:45,174
I know.

571
00:37:46,000 --> 00:37:50,866
When she gets married, I will let her know.

572
00:37:51,550 --> 00:37:56,295
Can you do it without me?

573
00:37:57,400 --> 00:37:59,382
I'm not sure.

574
00:37:59,382 --> 00:38:01,042
Mother.

575
00:38:01,042 --> 00:38:04,006
I made milk tea. Can you drink?

576
00:38:04,006 --> 00:38:06,067
Thank you.

577
00:38:06,850 --> 00:38:11,930
Therefore, I made a promise to tell you when you get married.

578
00:38:15,690 --> 00:38:19,284
It smells great.

579
00:38:19,284 --> 00:38:22,170
However, you said that you do not want to get married.

580
00:38:25,000 --> 00:38:27,176
Are you disappointed?

581
00:38:29,160 --> 00:38:31,299
No, I'm shocked.

582
00:38:33,010 --> 00:38:36,019
Do people get married this way?

583
00:38:41,140 --> 00:38:42,864
However...

584
00:38:43,920 --> 00:38:46,328
I was very happy.

585
00:38:49,560 --> 00:38:53,402
I found a gem that I could not have found elsewhere.

586
00:38:55,330 --> 00:38:57,605
Father.

587
00:39:01,190 --> 00:39:05,363
I also managed to become a father.

588
00:39:07,540 --> 00:39:09,691
Therefore, I also hope that

589
00:39:10,920 --> 00:39:13,562
you can live your life to the fullest.

590
00:39:17,560 --> 00:39:19,526
Father.

591
00:39:22,320 --> 00:39:26,591
Thank you for getting married with Mother.

592
00:39:30,120 --> 00:39:32,554
Finally...

593
00:39:33,490 --> 00:39:37,245
I understand the meaning of marriage.

594
00:39:39,140 --> 00:39:43,598
You only know it now?

595
00:39:45,450 --> 00:39:46,985
Here you go.

596
00:40:03,160 --> 00:40:05,226
Actually,

597
00:40:05,940 --> 00:40:10,008
Kyoka is not related by blood to me.

598
00:40:11,900 --> 00:40:16,656
I will let her know about it, but I'm not sure how she will take it.

599
00:40:17,330 --> 00:40:20,848
Why did you tell me such an important matter?

600
00:40:20,848 --> 00:40:25,416
I became her father,

601
00:40:27,190 --> 00:40:31,730
and I'm happy to do that.

602
00:40:33,590 --> 00:40:36,635
She's my daughter.

603
00:40:38,100 --> 00:40:39,795
Therefore,

604
00:40:40,970 --> 00:40:45,009
I hope that you can believe in her.

605
00:41:09,169 --> 00:41:11,608
<i>[Moon Night Yoga]</i>

606
00:41:29,850 --> 00:41:34,140
<i>[Moon Night Yoga]</i>

607
00:41:37,340 --> 00:41:40,132
- Good evening.
- Good evening.

608
00:41:40,132 --> 00:41:43,957
Please place your mat at your desired spot.

609
00:41:48,270 --> 00:41:50,568
<i>Sorry, the meeting is extended.</i>

610
00:41:50,568 --> 00:41:52,350
<i>I won't be able to make it for the lesson.</i>

611
00:41:52,350 --> 00:41:55,016
<i>If it ends early, I will be there.</i>

612
00:41:59,950 --> 00:42:03,928
Point your feet to the floor,

613
00:42:03,928 --> 00:42:06,625
and face the front.

614
00:42:06,625 --> 00:42:10,779
Lower your tailbone and lift your arms up.

615
00:42:12,420 --> 00:42:14,869
This is the crescent pose.

616
00:42:17,200 --> 00:42:18,700
Excuse me. I'll take my leave first.

617
00:42:18,700 --> 00:42:20,570
Goodbye.

618
00:42:21,780 --> 00:42:25,753
The full moon slowly reduces in size.

619
00:42:26,480 --> 00:42:29,664
Everything is ever-changing,

620
00:42:30,340 --> 00:42:34,469
Including shaped and shapeless things.

621
00:42:35,120 --> 00:42:38,700
Of course, that includes yourself, too.

622
00:42:39,490 --> 00:42:42,921
You laugh and you cry.

623
00:42:43,460 --> 00:42:49,943
Your heart gets shaken, and time itself is transient.

624
00:42:51,000 --> 00:42:56,001
Or rather, your heart needs to continue beating,

625
00:42:56,001 --> 00:42:59,337
even though you are a calm person.

626
00:43:01,430 --> 00:43:09,600
That means, a change is equal to the meaning of living.

627
00:43:09,600 --> 00:43:15,405
Not everything goes accordingly to your plan,

628
00:43:17,770 --> 00:43:22,684
things that you have not thought of happens in a normal day.

629
00:43:22,684 --> 00:43:26,629
Let's make the most out of our lives.

630
00:43:36,880 --> 00:43:38,818
Old lady, I'll help you.

631
00:43:38,818 --> 00:43:42,086
- I'll carry it.
- Thank you.

632
00:43:56,240 --> 00:44:04,820
credits

633
00:44:06,590 --> 00:44:08,647
Kyoka-chan, well done.

634
00:44:09,180 --> 00:44:10,687
Thank you.

635
00:44:21,770 --> 00:44:23,328
Kyoka-chan.

636
00:44:23,950 --> 00:44:25,673
Let's get married.

637
00:44:26,560 --> 00:44:27,708
What?

638
00:44:27,708 --> 00:44:30,169
Let's go to Malaysia together.

639
00:44:31,000 --> 00:44:33,006
Are you serious?

640
00:44:33,006 --> 00:44:34,958
Of course.

641
00:44:34,958 --> 00:44:38,176
My legs are trembling now.

642
00:44:42,160 --> 00:44:44,913
Kyoka-chan, you are my miracle.

643
00:44:45,760 --> 00:44:48,576
You are the first person that I really like.

644
00:44:49,620 --> 00:44:52,226
I liked you when I was a child,

645
00:44:52,226 --> 00:44:54,530
but I like you even more now.

646
00:44:56,490 --> 00:44:59,160
I will be your wife.

647
00:45:00,890 --> 00:45:04,556
To be a good wife after marriage,

648
00:45:04,556 --> 00:45:07,496
that's what you are worried about.

649
00:45:08,850 --> 00:45:12,954
You can just be yourself, just lazy or careless.

650
00:45:14,240 --> 00:45:17,653
I want to become a person like your mother.

651
00:45:18,180 --> 00:45:20,186
You don't need to change anything.

652
00:45:20,186 --> 00:45:23,889
Just do your yoga, and always be happy.

653
00:45:29,320 --> 00:45:32,516
When I went to your house last time,

654
00:45:32,516 --> 00:45:35,834
I felt lonely when I said "Thanks for inviting me."

655
00:45:35,834 --> 00:45:39,888
I want to say "I'm back" instead.

656
00:45:40,590 --> 00:45:42,407
Kyoka-chan,

657
00:45:48,510 --> 00:45:51,116
I want to be your real family.

658
00:45:52,980 --> 00:45:54,482
Family?

659
00:45:56,280 --> 00:45:59,050
A family member does not change like a lover.

660
00:45:59,740 --> 00:46:02,380
I will always treat you with importance.

661
00:46:02,380 --> 00:46:08,050
♫ <i>I want you alone to reflect yourself</i> ♫

662
00:46:08,050 --> 00:46:13,620
♫ <i>My hands falter, but I do my best</i> ♫

663
00:46:13,620 --> 00:46:21,290
♫ <i>To capture you with it</i> ♫

664
00:46:23,000 --> 00:46:24,576
<i>[Final episode]</i>

665
00:46:24,576 --> 00:46:27,087
Thank you... for marrying me.
<i>[A love miracle - 34 years relationship as father and daughter]</i>

666
00:46:27,087 --> 00:46:28,810
We will become a real family...
<i>[A love miracle - 34 years relationship as father and daughter]</i>

667
00:46:28,810 --> 00:46:31,138
- You're late.
- It's already late.

668
00:46:31,138 --> 00:46:33,076
Sorry, I can't marry you.
